          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "IOCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The fission fragments were detected with",
                "a delta-E - E telescope, which consisted of a",
                "ionization chamber divided into two parts by a grid.",
                "The entire chamber was filled to ~200 Torr with a",
                "Ar + 10% CH4 mixture. The telescope has a",
                "mean Z (charge) resolving power Z/AZ of -40."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " To get the dependence of delta E on Z and E",
                " the spectra were analyzed by putting a",
                " window on the fragment energy (2MeV wide)."
              ]
            }
          ],
